242
00:12:19,390 --> 00:12:22,930
Yokozuna Kawamatsu

A Kozuki Clan Retainer

243
00:12:22,970 --> 00:12:24,350
Kawamatsu!

244
00:12:25,530 --> 00:12:26,840
Is that Kiku?!

245
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:30,780
You have not changed a bit!

246
00:12:30,780 --> 00:12:33,680
I am so glad to see you alive!

247
00:12:33,680 --> 00:12:35,420
Raizo, I feel the same.

248
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:37,780
Huh?! Kiku! When did you arrive?!

249
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:42,170
What's going on?!
Who's that guy with a giant face?!

250
00:12:42,170 --> 00:12:47,200
He's an intruder! He stole the keys
and the sword from the tower!

251
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:51,550
What the hell are you waiting for?!
Seize them already!

252
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:53,170
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

253
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:07,520
What the hell did you come back for?!

254
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:09,310
Kawamatsu...

255
00:13:09,310 --> 00:13:11,830
Are you okay, my friend?

256
00:13:13,190 --> 00:13:16,940
I must apologize. I feel I am about
to lose thirteen years of lunches.

257
00:13:20,860 --> 00:13:25,330
Prepare the plague rounds!
Let's finish them off!

258
00:13:25,730 --> 00:13:28,120
Everyone, prepare for battle!

259
00:13:31,050 --> 00:13:33,080
Step away from Luffytaro!

260
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:35,920
Kiku! Raizo!

261
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:37,870
Leopard

262
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:37,870
HYO

263
00:13:39,990 --> 00:13:42,340
Whoa! Gramps!

264
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:46,430
What...? Could you really be Boss Hyogoro?!

265
00:13:46,430 --> 00:13:50,770
Indeed. But more importantly... Kiku! Raizo!

266
00:13:51,560 --> 00:13:54,640
Tell them who you are!

267
00:13:55,890 --> 00:14:02,320
There are those with broken spirits,
and there are those who have fought and lost.

268
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:07,020
If you wish to inspire them, you must
remove those cloth face coverings!

269
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:10,420
You speak the truth,

270
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:12,000
Boss Hyogoro.

271
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:14,250
How right you are.

272
00:14:14,250 --> 00:14:16,630
We must first earn their trust.

273
00:14:18,970 --> 00:14:24,590
If we do not reveal our identities,
we are no more than ghosts...

274
00:14:49,530 --> 00:14:51,500
It can't be...! That mask...!

275
00:14:53,650 --> 00:14:56,670
Wasn't he a warrior who
died at Oden Castle...?

276
00:14:56,670 --> 00:14:59,620
The most beautiful swordsman in Wano...

277
00:15:00,710 --> 00:15:02,880
Kikunojo of the Lingering Snow?!

278
00:15:02,880 --> 00:15:05,510
What?! You're a man?!

279
00:15:06,250 --> 00:15:07,760
I am a woman at heart.

280
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:09,430
That mask is scary!

281
00:15:10,950 --> 00:15:11,810
And that's...

282
00:15:12,620 --> 00:15:16,770
Fukurokuju's rival ninja, Raizo of the Mist!

283
00:15:16,770 --> 00:15:22,690
And there's the samurai Yokozuna Kawamatsu,
the greatest sumo wrestler of all time!

284
00:15:22,690 --> 00:15:28,660
That old man alongside them must be
the real Hyogoro the Flower!

285
00:15:30,720 --> 00:15:31,950
So...

286
00:15:31,950 --> 00:15:35,410
who the hell is Luffytaro?

287
00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:41,170
Whatever, that's an amazing group!

288
00:15:41,170 --> 00:15:44,210
What?! What about me?!

289
00:15:46,050 --> 00:15:49,680
This has turned out just like
Lord Orochi's ravings!

290
00:15:49,680 --> 00:15:53,430
We've got to warn Viceroy Kaido somehow!

291
00:15:53,430 --> 00:15:53,930
No...

292
00:15:56,050 --> 00:16:01,900
Now that you have seen us,
you will need to stay silent.

293
00:16:05,140 --> 00:16:06,490
Take them down!

294
00:16:10,740 --> 00:16:13,950
Ninpo: Flower Shuriken!

295
00:16:31,510 --> 00:16:34,780
Heavy Gong!

296
00:16:35,970 --> 00:16:38,000
Gum-Gum...

297
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,980
Gatling!

298
00:16:45,030 --> 00:16:47,480
Eat this plague round!

299
00:16:50,910 --> 00:16:51,700
What?!

300
00:16:57,130 --> 00:17:00,560
We can't hit him with the plague rounds,
Vice Warden Daifugo!

301
00:17:00,560 --> 00:17:03,340
I told you idiots it doesn't matter who they hit!

302
00:17:05,690 --> 00:17:09,760
You bastards! First you starve the prisoners,
and now you're shooting them!

303
00:17:10,690 --> 00:17:13,550
I can't let you use a virus as a weapon!

304
00:17:16,340 --> 00:17:19,390
Hold it! We won't let you get
in Vice Warden Daifugo's way!

305
00:17:19,390 --> 00:17:20,920
Let's go, Chopper!

306
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:21,900
All right!

307
00:17:24,310 --> 00:17:25,940
Gum-Gum...

308
00:17:27,530 --> 00:17:29,780
Heavy Stamp!

309
00:17:34,910 --> 00:17:37,200
Leave our countrymen alone!

310
00:17:46,130 --> 00:17:48,420
As he said!

311
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:56,390
It's a demon!

312
00:17:56,390 --> 00:17:58,560
Kappa Style...

313
00:18:03,230 --> 00:18:04,980
Yorikiri!

314
00:18:15,490 --> 00:18:18,860
Ninpo: Lightning Shuriken!

315
00:18:40,970 --> 00:18:44,220
Use these, friend of Master Luffy.

316
00:18:44,220 --> 00:18:46,000
Friend?!

317
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:48,600
One of them should work.

318
00:18:58,020 --> 00:18:59,150
Damn!

319
00:18:59,150 --> 00:19:00,940
I've been shot!

320
00:19:01,730 --> 00:19:04,050
It's hot! It's so hot!

321
00:19:05,070 --> 00:19:07,150
Help me or it'll spread!

322
00:19:07,150 --> 00:19:08,170
Stay away from me!

323
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:12,050
Ahh, hot, hot, hot!

324
00:19:12,800 --> 00:19:17,360
Damn, those bastards are just
aiming at the prisoners!

325
00:19:25,830 --> 00:19:28,650
Oh, that's right. I forgot to mention one thing.

326
00:19:28,650 --> 00:19:32,070
The disease's name.

327
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:37,860
A high fever spreads from
where the bullet hits.

328
00:19:38,560 --> 00:19:42,160
Burning pain radiates across the body.

329
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:42,160
Ahh, it's hot!

330
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:45,080
Victims spew blood.

331
00:19:45,080 --> 00:19:49,460
Then they suffer and wriggle about...

332
00:19:50,010 --> 00:19:55,340
and infect others with
that pain indiscriminately!

333
00:19:56,210 --> 00:19:58,540
Help me...!

334
00:19:58,540 --> 00:19:59,640
Stop that!

335
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:01,540
I'm in so much pain...!

336
00:20:01,540 --> 00:20:02,920
Let go!

337
00:20:04,780 --> 00:20:06,230
Behold!

338
00:20:06,230 --> 00:20:10,170
That's what becomes of the infected!

339
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:14,020
Help me...

340
00:20:18,620 --> 00:20:24,320
They're like dried-up, rotten plants!

341
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:37,260
Help me...

342
00:20:37,260 --> 00:20:39,200
Stay back. Don't come close.

343
00:20:44,930 --> 00:20:46,700
That's...

344
00:20:47,540 --> 00:20:50,180
His Awesomeness Queen's masterpiece!

345
00:20:50,180 --> 00:20:54,340
This plague is called Mummy!

346
00:21:01,410 --> 00:21:02,450
Go!

347
00:21:03,250 --> 00:21:09,290
You are now human weapons capable
of defeating enemies with a single touch!

348
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:12,710
We can't let the virus spread!

349
00:21:12,710 --> 00:21:15,510
Everyone, you need to stop moving!

350
00:21:15,510 --> 00:21:17,070
I'll handle this somehow!

351
00:21:17,070 --> 00:21:20,470
I will cure every one of you!

352
00:21:20,470 --> 00:21:22,340
The rest of you should get moving!

353
00:21:22,940 --> 00:21:24,970
Or should I consider you rebels?

354
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:31,270
Dammit!

355
00:21:34,530 --> 00:21:35,690
They're not stopping!

356
00:21:36,590 --> 00:21:37,570
In the end,

357
00:21:37,570 --> 00:21:41,950
everyone in Udon is against us!

358
00:21:43,760 --> 00:21:45,530
Get outta here!

359
00:21:49,530 --> 00:21:51,920
If you hadn't come...

360
00:21:53,500 --> 00:21:58,050
we'd have never met this fate!

361
00:21:58,050 --> 00:22:01,550
Even if you guys really are...

362
00:22:02,820 --> 00:22:09,720
the Red Scabbard samurai... who were
thought to have died twenty years ago...

363
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:12,270
you'll never win!

364
00:22:13,730 --> 00:22:15,110
Kaido...!

365
00:22:15,900 --> 00:22:19,480
That giant flying dragon...!

366
00:22:20,710 --> 00:22:23,670
The Beast Pirates...!

367
00:22:23,670 --> 00:22:25,870
No one can defeat them!

368
00:22:28,410 --> 00:22:29,540
Look at us...

369
00:22:30,050 --> 00:22:37,050
Just one of Kaido's subordinates
created this single weapon...

370
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:40,420
and brought this menace!

371
00:22:42,220 --> 00:22:45,890
Its power is devastating!

372
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:53,200
That's right! If you strangers hadn't come...

373
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:57,770
we'd have been able to maintain
our daily routine here in Udon!

374
00:22:59,900 --> 00:23:04,140
We'd have never had to go through this!

375
00:23:16,340 --> 00:23:18,290
No, Luffytaro! Don't touch them!

376
00:23:28,270 --> 00:23:32,970
Stop! All of you!

377
00:23:32,970 --> 00:23:35,850
You idiot! You infected yourself!

378
00:23:52,570 --> 00:23:53,540
Is he stupid?!

379
00:23:58,060 --> 00:23:59,070
Stop already!

380
00:23:59,070 --> 00:24:00,420
You'll die!

381
00:24:01,460 --> 00:24:04,170
What are you doing, Master Luffytaro?!

382
00:24:11,310 --> 00:24:12,850
Sir Straw Hat!

383
00:24:17,100 --> 00:24:19,190
What "menace"?!

384
00:24:23,120 --> 00:24:26,860
"Its power is devastating"?!

385
00:24:28,180 --> 00:24:29,570
This disease...

386
00:24:30,170 --> 00:24:32,530
doesn't hurt me at all!

387
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:35,810
Liar!

388
00:24:35,810 --> 00:24:37,750
Get away from them now!

389
00:24:37,750 --> 00:24:39,500
Luffy!

390
00:24:47,540 --> 00:24:52,470
Every samurai I've met is as tough as hell!

391
00:25:08,950 --> 00:25:12,060
But you guys...!

392
00:25:12,060 --> 00:25:15,490
Your spirit has been shattered!

393
00:25:21,080 --> 00:25:23,210
Living your "daily routine"?!

394
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:28,630
They tell you what to do,
and you get your stupid dumplings...!

395
00:25:31,290 --> 00:25:36,560
They give you just enough to survive,
and you call that living?!

396
00:25:52,170 --> 00:25:53,700
Wake up!

397
00:25:54,530 --> 00:25:56,330
You know what that makes you?!

398
00:25:56,850 --> 00:25:58,780
Slaves!

399
00:26:06,600 --> 00:26:09,160
Big Bro and the others are okay!

400
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:11,460
Are they really okay...?

401
00:26:14,570 --> 00:26:18,890
What's wrong with me
coming from another country?!

402
00:26:19,360 --> 00:26:23,020
What's wrong with a stranger
defending this land?!

403
00:26:38,380 --> 00:26:40,750
I made a promise!

404
00:26:43,410 --> 00:26:46,960
I promised... my friend...

405
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:50,710
who gave me her own food in Kuri!

406
00:26:51,450 --> 00:26:56,510
I will make this a country
where everyone can eat their fill!

407
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:03,100
I'm gonna make this normal for you!

408
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:07,660
Before we leave this country,

409
00:27:07,660 --> 00:27:11,480
I'll make it a place where you can
eat as much as you want!

410
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:16,910
Big Bro...

411
00:27:16,910 --> 00:27:19,240
I'm gonna keep that promise...!

412
00:27:20,710 --> 00:27:25,210
If I don't... this country will be...

413
00:27:25,210 --> 00:27:27,750
an eternal hell!

414
00:27:36,130 --> 00:27:38,490
I heard about Oden.

415
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:41,180
He was amazing!

416
00:27:42,710 --> 00:27:48,400
But on the day Kaido
killed him twenty years ago...

417
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:52,070
this country stopped moving forward!

418
00:27:57,060 --> 00:28:02,050
We came to defeat Kaido!

419
00:28:03,150 --> 00:28:08,120
We don't need allies who just get our way!

420
00:28:13,170 --> 00:28:16,380
So, now's the time for you to decide!

421
00:28:17,090 --> 00:28:18,780
Are you with us?!

422
00:28:19,740 --> 00:28:22,180
Or with Kaido?!

423
00:28:31,120 --> 00:28:32,520
Are you serious?

424
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:45,820
You'd give us...

425
00:28:47,330 --> 00:28:49,090
another chance?

426
00:29:04,520 --> 00:29:06,120
He's won their hearts!

427
00:29:07,810 --> 00:29:10,100
What a commanding presence!

428
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:13,310
We've got a problem.

429
00:29:14,300 --> 00:29:17,280
He's gone and stirred their hearts.

430
00:29:17,750 --> 00:29:22,370
But if I fire a shot right now
while their guard is down,

431
00:29:22,370 --> 00:29:24,780
they'll all panic...

432
00:29:25,380 --> 00:29:27,910
flipping the situation in our favor.

433
00:29:28,540 --> 00:29:33,380
I'll scatter 200 plague rounds
worth of the virus

434
00:29:33,380 --> 00:29:35,340
using this plague shot!

435
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:42,430
Eat a big bowl of elephant snot!

436
00:29:43,890 --> 00:29:46,370
No way, Warden! That's too much!

437
00:29:48,440 --> 00:29:50,350
No, please don't!

438
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:57,550
Hey, Babanuki looks like he's
about to fire something over here.

439
00:29:57,550 --> 00:29:58,480
What?!

440
00:30:00,950 --> 00:30:02,160
It's too late!

441
00:30:08,790 --> 00:30:12,740
Elephant Achoo!

442
00:30:20,170 --> 00:30:21,410
What?!

443
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:25,140
What?! What?! What?!

444
00:30:28,380 --> 00:30:31,430
I had to. I saw a pretty bad future.

445
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:46,660
Warden Babanuki!

446
00:30:46,660 --> 00:30:49,170
Warden!

447
00:30:56,890 --> 00:30:58,210
What a...

448
00:31:00,590 --> 00:31:02,840
formidable man he is...!

449
00:31:05,050 --> 00:31:06,390
The rest is up to you.

450
00:31:15,380 --> 00:31:16,900
We'll handle it!

451
00:31:16,900 --> 00:31:19,820
Hey, wait! You better remember!

452
00:31:20,290 --> 00:31:22,740
What happens if you defy the guards?!

453
00:31:22,740 --> 00:31:26,160
First, we cut off both your arms!

454
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:28,240
We know, and we don't care.

455
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:32,500
We've already decided to revolt!

456
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:36,930
This is payback for all these years...!

457
00:31:36,930 --> 00:31:38,500
Here we go!

458
00:31:37,980 --> 00:31:38,500
Yeah!

459
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:52,640
Eight days until the final battle...

460
00:31:54,290 --> 00:31:57,600
Unbeknownst to the enemy's main army...

